Class Ammo

  • java.lang.Object
    • Ammo

  • public class Ammo
extends java.lang.Object
    The Ammo class is represented by the Apple icon and if falls to the bottom of the screen and when the player captures this object it gives him more ammunition to shoot the bad guys. Created by Ankur on 4/24/2015.
